   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Helping scavengers children in Bali</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">About 15 minutes drive from Kuta is Bali&apos;s biggest official tip at Suwung, where mountains of rubbish dominate the landscape. It&apos;s a 30 Hectare Trash Mountain Site.This area is also a home for 100 plus families who work in this area by sorting trash by hands, who most of them coming from Various area of Indonesia. Many of the families can&apos;t afford to school the their children as the results of a very small income.We help through education, empowerment, medical support and other assistant.</narrative>
  </description>
